Which file contains a message that is displayed after successful login?
A)  /etc/loginbanner
B)  /etc/issue
C)  /etc/motd
D)  /etc/message
C
C. The contents of the file motd, an abbreviation for Message of the Day, are displayedwhen a user logs in successfully. Among the other options, the contents of /etc/issueare displayed prior to local login. The other filenames are not valid for this purpose.
